title: John Frieda Sheer Blonde Go Blonder Controlled Lightening Spray, 3.5 Ounce
description: Versatile, patent-pending formula with citrus and chamomile works with styling heat to gradually lighten and brighten for a natural-looking, blonder blonde. Contains thermo-protectant.
